1","tid":2126010,"uid":276497,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"真心識人，講科技野政府完全係垃圾級，多做多錯少做少錯嘅心態<br />\n點會批你真係搞數據中心，劈頭第一句就話：「係咪有咁嘅需要？」之後接多句「現有設施係咪做唔到先？」，9成it野都冇得搞"},{"pid":"935c7187447b9f696f0b831c42875904df5f1d0e","tid":2126010,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a978baf267334ceb841e4669b447bc085334e68c","tid":2126010,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/821/1*KpZGO-x3nrs4zdHzkx3pnw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F821%2F1%2AKpZGO-x3nrs4zdHzkx3pnw.png&h=b0dd4633&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:35:54.000Z","msg":"藍絲嚟?"},{"pid":"f901b06d70d6fd71e5944eb5fdae556c80d7bab8","tid":2126010,"uid":271431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"IT當地產咁搞.."},{"pid":"da5a01ea9d9a07e4f9a854007748eff7ac264bc5","tid":2126010,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"935c7187447b9f696f0b831c42875904df5f1d0e","tid":2126010,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a978baf267334ceb841e4669b447bc085334e68c","tid":2126010,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/821/1*KpZGO-x3nrs4zdHzkx3pnw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F821%2F1%2AKpZGO-x3nrs4zdHzkx3pnw.png&h=b0dd4633&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:35:54.000Z","msg":"藍絲嚟?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/104469819_P8qUi_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih